Syntax: detox

Attempts to purge poison from your system through sheer physical endurance
and trained resistance. Detox is a passive/active skill available to rogues
and certain combat classes.

Success at removing poison depends on your learned proficiency in the skill.
At higher skill levels, detox is more reliably effective. Unlike the magical
"cure poison" spell, detox requires no mana and works through physical
training alone.

Use detox as soon as you notice a poison effect to prevent ongoing damage.

Requirements:
  - Must have the Detox skill learned.
  - Must be poisoned (or the skill will have no effect).

See also: shelp detox cure poison poison
